data.message: As a member of the Navy SEALS community and a part of one of these organizations this is highly offensive. SEALS in the US Armed Forces make it their goal to get over 300 confirmed kills as well as conduct numerous secret raids on Al-Quaeda. Comparing gorilla warfare to a dead gorilla from a meme on the internet is absurd and beyond inaccurate. Making the claim that Special Ops are cliques is demeaning the brotherhood and values they are founded on. This clearly is a stab at a branch of the US Armed Forces that does nothing but support the rest of the nation, kiddo.

Ως μέλος της ελληνικής κοινότητας και ένα μέρος ενός από αυτούς τους οργανισμούς είναι ιδιαίτερα προσβλητικό. Αδελφότητες στο UC Berkeley το στόχο τους να προσφέρουν στις γυναίκες ένα μέρος για να αισθάνονται άνετα, καθώς και καλύτερη η κοινότητα κάνει. Συγκρίνοντας ειδικά σπίτια για να τους χαρακτήρες από μια ταινία για τον εκφοβισμό είναι παράλογο και πέρα ανακριβές. Κάνοντας τον ισχυρισμό ότι αδελφότητες είναι κλίκες είναι μειωτικό την αδελφότητα και τις αξίες που βασίζονται σε. Αυτό είναι σαφώς μια μαχαιριά σε μια κοινότητα στην πανεπιστημιούπολη που δεν κάνει τίποτα, αλλά υποστηρίζουν το υπόλοιπο του φοιτητικού σώματος.

data.message: dirks pls

What the fuck did you just fucking say about me, you little EECS major? I’ll have you know I graduated top of my sorority in Alpha Phi, and I’ve been involved in numerous fundraisers for charity, and I have over 300 confirmed bids. I am trained in business management and I’m the top E-Board member in the entire chapter. You are nothing to me but just another nerd. I will wipe you the fuck out with a community the likes of which have never been seen before on this Earth, mark my words. You think you can get away with saying that shit to me over the UC Berkeley Memes for Edgy Teens page? Think again, fucker. As we speak I am contacting my secret network of sisters across the chapter and your scent is being traced right now so you better prepare for the storm, nerd. The storm that wipes out the pathetic thing you call your body odor. You’re fucking excluded, nerd. I can be highly offended any time, and can bully you in over seven hundred ways, and that’s just with my clique. Not only am I extensively connected, but I have access to my entire network of alumni of Alpha Phi members and I will use it to its full extent to wipe your miserable memes off the face of the internet, you little geek. If only you could have known what unholy retribution your little “clever” meme was about to bring down upon you, maybe you would have held your fucking tongue. But you couldn’t, you didn’t, and now you’re paying the price, you goddamn EECS major. I will shit sisterhood all over you and you will drown in it. You’re fucking absurd and beyond inaccurate, kiddo.
